node.text: Huge butterflies (and an excited 👶🏼) in my stomach 🦋 My next book is nearly done 🍫📕🎉 It’s part two of #majaschokolade and all about chocolate tarts. Out this autumn both in Danish and English. Send me some ❤️ to help me finish the book before baby arrives 🙈 #blackcurrantbrownietarts 🌀
